{"type":"message","id":"a6faa11f","parentId":"5513f3c3","timestamp":"2026-04-03T08:34:39.327Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-baa628f235944819","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"value\": {\n    \"summary\": [\n      \"These sources provide a comprehensive masterclass on **OpenClaw**, an open-source platform designed to transform AI from a simple chatbot into an **autonomous business operations system**. The material outlines a transition from manual task management to a **multi-agent workforce** capable of handling outreach, specialized meetings, and automated sales. Key technical modules focus on **security hardening**, cost reduction through **token optimization**, and a sophisticated **memory architecture** that prevents AI instructions from decaying over time. The guide introduces a **\\\"Builder-Orchestrator-Executor\\\"** framework to separate high-level management from technical construction and task performance. Additionally, it explores the future of **agent-to-agent commerce**, where AI entities autonomously transact using blockchain technology. Ultimately, the content serves as a blueprint for entrepreneurs to replace expensive SaaS subscriptions with a **self-evolving AI infrastructure**.\"\n    ],\n    \"suggested_topics\": []\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":4571,"aggregated":"{\n  \"value\": {\n    \"summary\": [\n      \"These sources provide a comprehensive masterclass on **OpenClaw**, an open-source platform designed to transform AI from a simple chatbot into an **autonomous business operations system**. The material outlines a transition from manual task management to a **multi-agent workforce** capable of handling outreach, specialized meetings, and automated sales. Key technical modules focus on **security hardening**, cost reduction through **token optimization**, and a sophisticated **memory architecture** that prevents AI instructions from decaying over time. The guide introduces a **\\\"Builder-Orchestrator-Executor\\\"** framework to separate high-level management from technical construction and task performance. Additionally, it explores the future of **agent-to-agent commerce**, where AI entities autonomously transact using blockchain technology. Ultimately, the content serves as a blueprint for entrepreneurs to replace expensive SaaS subscriptions with a **self-evolving AI infrastructure**.\"\n    ],\n    \"suggested_topics\": []\n  }\n}","cwd":"/home/ivo/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775205279324}}
