{"type":"message","id":"0a168919","parentId":"9715d3b2","timestamp":"2026-04-04T23:13:19.954Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hey Ivek! 👋 Good to see you. We're in the middle of **Step 9: Mission Control Dashboard** for your OpenClaw setup. Last I checked, you needed to decide on the approach:\n\n1. **Use Lovable** (vibe coding platform) — paste the ClawBuddy LiteKit prompt to generate the dashboard UI shell\n2. **Build locally** — I create a React/Vite dashboard in your workspace that connects to OpenClaw's CLI\n\nWhich direction do you want to go? Or is there something else on your mind?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"z-ai/glm5","usage":{"input":60375,"output":118,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60493,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775344369873,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ac4bc5a64982d787"}}
