{"type":"message","id":"e4f690ea","parentId":"d3908b09","timestamp":"2026-04-07T06:02:31.079Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-a152aaf78e1e2d77","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.5 (3e72c03)\n   I don't just autocomplete—I auto-commit (emotionally), then ask you to review (logically).\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage.\n\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"tidy-wharf","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.5 (3e72c03)\n   I don't just autocomplete—I auto-commit (emotionally), then ask you to review (logically).\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage.\n\n","name":"openclaw cron"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775541751076}}
