{"type":"message","id":"909bc6cd","parentId":"8bdcf208","timestamp":"2026-04-07T06:25:07.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We need to complete the GitHub auth process. The user needs to follow the prompts in their terminal/browser to authenticate. Since this is an interactive process, I should instruct them to complete it. However, I can't see the output or interact with the browser from here. I'll inform them that the auth process has started and they need to complete it. Let me also check if there's a way to proceed with the plan while waiting for auth. Actually, I should wait for them to complete the auth step before moving on, as subsequent steps depend on it. I'll provide guidance.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"I've started the GitHub authentication process. **You need to complete it now:**\n\n1. A browser window should have opened (or will open shortly)\n2. Log in to your GitHub account if prompted\n3. Authorize the GitHub CLI to access your account\n4. Once authorized, return here and confirm\n\n**While you do that, I'll prepare the next steps:**\n\nOnce GitHub auth is done, we'll:\n- Create a GitHub repo for your Vercel dashboard\n- Connect it so you can version control your ClawBuddy dashboard\n- Set up browser control verification\n- Configure AgentMail for email automation\n- Install your first skill from playbooks.com\n\nPlease complete the GitHub auth now, then let me know when it's done! 🔐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b","usage":{"input":115061,"output":284,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115345,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775543087260,"responseId":"chatcmpl-896f2a45f576649b"}}
