{"type":"compaction","id":"1c021c03","parentId":"3d302442","timestamp":"2026-04-18T17:29:43.931Z","summary":"## Goal\n1. Complete OpenClaw\n 23-step setup (currently at Step 10: Integrations & Skills Ecosystem)\n2. Tidy up ClawBuddy dashboard by removing all OpenClaw logos, mentions, and branding\n3. Weather queries for Postojna, Slovenia (auxiliary — completed)\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Ivek prefers vibe coding tools (Lovable, Claude Code, Codex) over traditional coding\n- Avoid n8n/Make/Zapier — moved to AI-first tools\n- Wants honest feedback, no fake encouragement\n- Ship first, talk second (SOUL.md rule)\n- Tables/complex formatting hard to read on Telegram — use simple lists\n- Browser tool is unavailable (timed out, gateway issue) — do NOT retry\n- Always read skill SKILL.md before installing (prompt injection risk)\n- Keep Supabase/API integration functional during rebranding (only change user-facing strings)\n- Reminders must be direct Telegram messages, not buried in heartbeat responses\n- Follow HEARTBEAT.md strictly on periodic checks\n- Agent identity: bbymama, 📈\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Step 8: Memory Architecture — `memoryFlush.enabled: true`, `sessionMemory: true`, `contextEngine.enabled: true` in openclaw.json\n- [x] ContextEngine enabled in openclaw.json\n- [x] Step 9: Mission Control Dashboard — live on Vercel at `https://ivofrankai-star-command-center-ai.vercel.app/`\n- [x] GitHub CLI authenticated as `ivofrankai-star` (device code flow)\n- [x] Dashboard local repo at `/home/ivo/.openclaw/workspace/command-center-ai/` with `.git` connected to `origin/main`\n- [x] `openclaw doctor --non-interactive` run — gateway and Telegram healthy; missing embedding API keys (voyage, mistral) non-blocking\n- [x] Step 10 execution plan created (GitHub auth, browser control, AgentMail, skills)\n- [x] Water reminder tasks created and completed on ClawBuddy (task API tested: create, list, move all work)\n- [x] Tidy-up plan written to `/home/ivo/.openclaw/workspace/PLAN_TIDY.md`\n- [x] Queried NotebookLM notebook `ba0ef6dc-240e-4342-bf69-5fb5f0398310` for Steps 8 and 9 details\n- [x] Fetched Postojna weather (clear, 8°C now, up to 17°C, zero rain)\n- [x] HEARTBEAT.md updated with ClawBuddy Dashboard integration tasks\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Step 10: Browser control verification (session lost after `openclaw browser status`)\n- [ ] Step 10: AgentMail setup (not started)\n- [ ] Step 10: Skills installation (not started)\n- [ ] Dashboard rebranding/tidying (plan created at PLAN_TIDY.md, execution pending approval)\n\n### Blocked\n- OpenClaw cron scheduling: `openclaw cron` exists but no job set up — timed reminders impossible without it\n- Browser tool unavailable/times out\n- `at` command not available on system\n- `curl` to wttr.in with full forecast format exits with code 52 (only `format=3` and JSON work)\n- Ivek has not explicitly approved tidy-up execution or Step 10 sub-tasks\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Used openclaw.json for config**: Added `compaction.memoryFlush.enabled`, `memorySearch.experimental.sessionMemory`, `contextEngine.enabled` — all `true`\n- **Lovable recommended for Step 9**: Dashboard built with Lovable, deployed to Vercel\n- **Builder-Orchestrator-Executor pattern**: Build once with right tool, orchestrate with OpenClaw, execute with specialized agents\n- **Task API uses `action: \"move\"` with `{id, column}`** for status changes (not `update` with `task_id`/`status`)\n- **Task API uses `action: \"create\"` with `{title, column, priority}`** for new tasks (not `task` field — causes null title)\n- **Reminder delivery**: Direct Telegram message, not mixed into heartbeat response\n- **Dashboard rebrand**: Remove OpenClaw branding from UI, keep Supabase integration intact\n- **ClawBuddy dashboard**: Dark glass-morphic theme, 5 tabs (Command Deck, Agent Profiles, Kanban Board, AI Log, Agent Council)\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Get Ivek's approval to execute tidy-up plan from PLAN_TIDY.md (backup → search & replace → test → deploy)\n2. Set up OpenClaw cron for scheduled reminders (e.g., daily 8:00 water reminder)\n3. Verify browser control in OpenClaw\n4. Set up AgentMail (signup, API key, `.env` config)\n5. Install first skill (read SKILL.md first, then `npx playbooks add skill`)\n6. Link dashboard to GitHub repo for version control & Vercel auto-deploys\n7. Continue remaining OpenClaw setup steps (11–23)\n\n## Critical Context\n- Workspace: `/home/ivo/.openclaw/workspace/`\n- Config file: `/home/ivo/.openclaw/workspace/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- OpenClaw version: `2026.4.1` (da64a97)\n- Dashboard Vercel URL: `https://ivofrankai-star-command-center-ai.vercel.app/`\n- Supabase URL: `https://hbjpjbaabyavlruvmkfx.supabase.co`\n- API endpoint: `curl -X POST \"${AGENT_COMMAND_API_URL}/functions/v1/ai-tasks\" -H \"x-webhook-secret: ${AGENT_COMMAND_WEBHOOK_SECRET}\" -H \"Content-Type: application/json\"`\n- Task API columns: `to_do`, `doing`, `needs_input`, `done`, `canceled`\n- Task API priorities: `low`, `medium`, `high`, `urgent`\n- Notebook ID: `ba0ef6dc-240e-4342-bf69-5fb5f0398310`\n- Source IDs: `89e7dd43-0d39-4e38-8e5c-014fd5c75584`, `8954446d-b965-4214-9f10-f8a8c4fbb713`\n- Masterclass prompts URL: `https://masterclass-prompts.netlify.app/clawbuddy-litekit`\n\n## Decisions\n- Memory flush + session memory search + context engine all enabled via openclaw.json\n- ClawBuddy dashboard: dark glass-morphic theme, 5 tabs\n- Builder-Orchestrator-Executor separation: build with Lovable/external, orchestrate with OpenClaw\n- Task API: `action: \"move\"` + `{id, column}` for status; `action: \"create\"` + `{title, column, priority}` for new tasks\n- Reminders as standalone Telegram messages, not in heartbeat cycles\n- Dashboard rebrand: remove OpenClaw branding, keep Supabase backend intact\n- Never let agent edit its own SOUL.md or IDENTITY.md (passivity drift risk)\n- Sub-agents can't see SOUL/IDENTITY/USER/MEMORY — encode context in AGENTS.md or task prompts\n- Backup `~/.openclaw` every 6 hours (cron) + weekly manual audit\n- SOUL.md under 100 lines, IDENTITY.md under 15 lines\n\n## Open TODOs\n- Execute tidy-up plan (remove OpenClaw logos/mentions from dashboard) — needs Ivek's approval\n- Set up OpenClaw cron for timed reminders\n- Verify browser control\n- Set up AgentMail\n- Install first skill (after reading SKILL.md)\n- Link dashboard repo to GitHub for version control\n- Complete remaining steps 11–23 of OpenClaw setup\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- Never let agent edit its own SOUL.md or IDENTITY.md (causes passivity drift)\n- Sub-agents can't see SOUL/IDENTITY/USER/MEMORY — encode context in AGENTS.md or task prompts\n- Backup `~/.openclaw` every 6 hours (cron) + weekly manual audit\n- SOUL.md must stay under 100 lines, IDENTITY.md under 15 lines\n- Browser tool is broken — do NOT retry, use alternative approaches\n- Always read SKILL.md before installing any skill (prompt injection risk)\n- Keep Supabase backend integration functional during rebrand\n- Follow HEARTBEAT.md strictly on periodic checks\n- If quiet 8+ hours → brief check-in\n- \"Push When Needed\": call out avoidance, refocus if scattered, nudge to build if only learning\n\n## Pending user asks\n- Ivek asked to tidy up dashboard (remove OpenClaw logos/mentions) — plan created at PLAN_TIDY.md, awaiting approval to execute\n- Ivek never explicitly chose to proceed with Step 10 sub-tasks (browser control, AgentMail, skills)\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- NotebookLM notebook: `ba0ef6dc-240e-4342-bf69-5fb5f0398310`\n- Source IDs: `89e7dd43-0d39-4e38-8e5c-014fd5c75584`, `8954446d-b965-4214-9f10-f8a8c4fbb713`\n- Notion DB: `33299624-0a66-818e-92d0-dabaca1c1ec8`\n- OpenClaw version: `2026.4.1` (da64a97)\n- Config path: `/home/ivo/.openclaw/workspace/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- Workspace: `/home/ivo/.openclaw/workspace/`\n- Dashboard local path: `/home/ivo/.openclaw/workspace/command-center-ai/`\n- Dashboard Vercel URL: `https://ivofrankai-star-command-center-ai.vercel.app